
'''= "an educational-ecological hangout for permaculture and sustainable agriculture" in Belgium.'''

URL: http://yggdra.be/


=Description=

"Yggdrasil is an educational-ecological hangout for permaculture and sustainable agriculture. Their research aims to provide advice and guidance for everyone wanting to grow food and herbs in a way that supports nature and is ecologically sustainable. To achieve this, they make their own garden available for observation upon appointment. They also provide workshops and courses for anyone who would like to learn how to grow their own food sustainably. In their courtyard, they have also constructed several smaller city gardens, which serve as an inspiration for those who do not have a lot of space."



